cd node-scripts
nvm use
npm ci

# create a new branch
git checkout scratch/my-awesome-feature
```

### Development

Make your desired changes and run the tests:

```bash
npm run build
npm run lint
npm test
```

The commit and push the changes to your branch and open a new pull request.

